Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:07.33,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}波に揺られてかたふりして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:12.21,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}進んでゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:16.71,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}宇宙（そら）より遠くへ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:53.97,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}悄悄寫下夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:58.55,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}找了一個又一個藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:04.18,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}就是從不著手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:08.90,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因為害怕改變
