Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我發現自己都高二了還一件都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,初中的時候你也什麼都沒做嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,才覺得高中三年一定得做點什麼才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得渾渾噩噩過日子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1252,34)}青春是等不來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1210,34)}勇氣 幹勁 活力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1168,34)}你能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1126,34)}布丁是飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1082,34)}想要保護你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1040,34)}不前進就不會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(996,34)}珍惜現在這個瞬間
Comment: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(954,34)}留下遺憾和後悔的高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,時間明明就很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時的決心到底哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你準備做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\c&H42433A&\pos(250,404)\frz32.31\fad(500,0)}揮灑青春。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我想實行一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\c&HCEDCC7&\pos(106,126)}1.表示建議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\c&HCEDCC7&\pos(564,564)}（去～怎麼樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,東京？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 先去東京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然後踏上沒有目的的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,隨心所向 浪跡天涯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoy your trip
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我要逃 逃學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,唔 也沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要請假啊 裝病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說 這點事沒什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,難不成你沒裝病請過假？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小惠你有過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 誰都會有過一兩次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,崇拜你！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼看我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那那 沒有目的的旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那就沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那那那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道我想問什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你會想的事情 用腳趾頭都能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.06,0:05:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事就是要一個人去才有意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想去就去唄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我會幫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.43,0:05:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,明天要在車站的洗手間換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.53,0:05:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 是大海 大海耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 群馬腔會被認出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這就要走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼背這麼大個包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 沒什麼 我跟朋友借了體操服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,別給我打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心 我已經幫你跟學校請過假了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,用這種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要在外面過夜 我會跟你統一口徑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你就放心去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在洗手間換好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,坐上和學校相反方向的電車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人跳出平時的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,踏上沒有目的的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,去往從未見過的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼會在這？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 今天下雨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說 還是覺得裝病請假不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒地方想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊 有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,京都 沖繩 北海道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼沒去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,飛機可能會掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,新幹線可能會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,還有可能天上砸隕石？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我向來這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,參加社團活動的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,學東西的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,想考好學校的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一到關鍵時刻我就發怵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,擔心從來沒做過的事要是沒做好怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.72,0:07:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得自己可能會後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,每次臨到頭來我就退縮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 我覺得也不算壞事就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 我不喜歡這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fs30\c&H232C28&\frz344.8\pos(602,274)}門禁之前我會回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fs30\c&H232C28&\frz344.8\pos(72,398)}家常蛋包飯做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我最討厭自己這一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下次出去玩吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你掉東西了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我數了一下 整整一百萬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,一百萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛帶來啊 應該交公吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我當時很慌…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,話怎麼說都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦 是真的 我真的很慌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 掉錢的人好像穿著我們學校的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,高幾？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那就不清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是掃到了一眼她的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好像…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她的頭髮跟那邊的女生差不多長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,估計是個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,還有呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 身上挺香的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是護髮素？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 頭髮那麼長的女生應該也沒幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我去高一教室看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好緊張…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,這股味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一百萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一百萬…元…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,一百萬…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,元！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn@FZZhunYuan-M02\frz270\fs30\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\pos(1060,210)\fad(300,0)}開關門{\3c&H32E8EB&}請輕聲!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（Partb）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊不 其實昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 別誤會 我不是偷的 只是碰巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,南極？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnSimHei\pos(760,130)\frz348.2\fs35}比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這本書是我媽媽寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她原來是個南極考察隊隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不過在我初中的時候失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,然後一直沒被找到 也幾乎沒留下什麼遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要去找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,去南極？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,去得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 朋友 老師 前輩和鄰居都說
