Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7\c&H504C8A&\bord1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(444,482)}會場：\N廣島縣吳市築地鎮\N吳港川原石南埠頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,廣島…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要麼說害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,明明就不可能去得了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那…你要不要一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 別因為是週六就睡懶覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這次真的要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,坐上和平時相反方向的電車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,去見從未見過的風景
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很想放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然可能沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:16.29,LINE,,0,0,0,,{\frz19.68\pos(940,112)}終於要去旅行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:23.05,LINE,,0,0,0,,{\frz12.43\pos(798,138)}拍到富士山了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼大啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,越過赤道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,穿過風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,破開冰層
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,去往日本的1萬4千公里之外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,比宇宙更加遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.94,0:23:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都無法靠近的那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你準備怎麼去？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,她揚起嘴角笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an7\bord0\c&H2F342D&\pos(328,394)\frz18.31}揮 灑 青 春 。
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的青春
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啟動了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:27.17,Default,,0,0,480,,{\bord1\c&H030007&\3c&HD3BE5E&\fad(0,1000)}比宇宙更遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,三宅 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
